{"tid":874853,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解成日出旺角見到港女打/鬧男朋友","createTime":"2018-10-24T13:31:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T15:35:09.000Z","uid":150079,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a2a1ed391f54a6853af85923658047e93a0c400a","tid":874853,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T13:31:13.000Z","msg":"之後連燈就會有一大堆港女沖入嚟話呢啲係少數例子，出街成日見到會唔會係少數例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本港女仲惡撚個共產黨，聽樓主講溝日本妹咪算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n港女仲溫柔過日本妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80bead51bb4e6219be836de046c8a7b2d62b71ba","tid":874853,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T13:33:42.000Z","msg":"根本港女就同共產黨一樣殺完人之後話從來冇8964呢件事，港女會講香港從來都冇港女，共產黨會講你唔明白中國嘅國情，港女會同你講呢啲係我地嘅真性情"},{"pid":"6f39d4576df180c33b39bd8e7bbcc21e03e522c8","tid":874853,"uid":150079,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T13:35:04.000Z","msg":"我喺日本住咗成年我就未見過日本妹鬧傑仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d026debd23445a932c0a8c7d44c00ca2c71f50","tid":874853,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T13:35:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我喺日本住咗成年我就未見過日本妹鬧條仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"973e7950b1b82cd4e1e22d62053aad87ee952aad","tid":874853,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T13:38:36.000Z","msg":"之後我幫港女講埋港女道理，費時佢哋又沖出嚟柒<br />\n乜嘢嘅人咪識返乜嘢嘅人囉<br />\n就係因為我咁溫柔咁好所以識返優質既日本妹<br />\n港女呢啲咁低質我係唔識唔到"},{"pid":"1045873fe5f882ff81611d69e8ced157c48488fb","tid":874853,"uid":27866,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T13:40:06.000Z","msg":"得啦，知喇。"},{"pid":"8bb50cd8d81a1010383037cc585552e0e9beeb4f","tid":874853,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T13: